hfind

A file listing command for HDFS filesystems similar to unix find(1).

Requires jruby.

# installation

Simply copy hfind.rb and hfind into your path.

# usage

usage: ./hfind.rb [options] path
  -h, --help
  -a, --after       # display files modified after ISO date
  -b, --before      # display files modified before ISO date
  -s, --size        # display files greater (+val) or less than (-val) size
  -l, --ls          # display full listing detail
  -u, --uri         # display full uri for path

Please let me know if you find this software useful!

--frank
